Package: BSPVTMWT
Version: 1.0
Maintainer: "Volker Bandke" <vbandke@bsp-gmbh.com>
Depends: MACLIB
Homepage: CBT Tape FILE 547
Description: Wait for VTAM ACB
 This routine waits for a VTAM ACB to become available.  The ACB
 name to be waited for is specified in the PARM keyword of the
 JCL EXEC Card

 This module can be used to start a VTAM application only if its
 related ACB is available

 SAMPLE EXECUTION JCL can be found in SYS2.SAMPLIB(BSPVTMWT)
